<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #fff5f8;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 0;
            color: #5d4a4a;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 30px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 4px solid #fce4ec;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(248, 187, 208, 0.3);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #fce4ec;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #d81b60;
            font-size: 28px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .order-card {
            background-color: #fff9fb;
            border: 2px dashed #f8bbd0;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .field {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #fce4ec;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #ad1457;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .value {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4a4a4a;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #f06292;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .cherry {
            color: #d81b60;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>New Order from {{}} ! 🧁</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Yay! You've got a new cake inquiry. Here are the lovely details:</p>
            
            <div class="order-card">
                <div class="field">
                    <span class="label">Customer Name</span>
                    <span class="value">{{name}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="field">
                    <span class="label">Email Address</span>
                    <span class="value">{{email}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="field">
                    <span class="label">Phone Number</span>
                    <span class="value">{{phone}}</span>
                </div>

                <div class="field">
                    <span class="label">Event Category</span>
                    <span class="value">{{eventType}}</span>
                </div>

                <div class="field" style="border-bottom: none;">
                    <span class="label">The Vision / Message</span>
                    <span class="value" style="display: block; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 5px;">
                        {{message}}
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <span class="cherry">🍒</span> Time to get baking!
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>